INSERT INTO `content_info` VALUES ('2512', '港圈初代男团近况悬殊：关智斌仍然活跃，搭档却成小网红的座上客', 'https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F0d7062b5p00qyxxcb00hrc000u000vpm.png&thumbnail=650x2147483647&quality=80&type=jpg', '0', '2021-09-06 08:07:26', '网易新闻', '0', '0', '1', '7', '<p id=\"083QTL0L\">提到港圈的初代偶像男团，Boy\'z组合肯定位于前列，由成员张致恒和关智斌组成，两人出道时20多岁，不仅拥有高颜值，还充满活泼阳光的气质，在当时大受欢迎。如今Boy\'z组合早已解散，两位成员的发展现状也是相差悬殊。</p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F0d7062b5p00qyxxcb00hrc000u000vpm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F57a5a050p00qyxxcc00n8c000u001a8m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p id=\"083QTL0P\">作为成员之一的关智斌，已到不惑之年，但整体状态保持良好，事业重心基本转移至内地，凭借《追鱼传奇》和《妻子的秘密》等热播剧赚足人气。之后虽无代表作问世，仍旧频频参加各类综艺，还与Twins合体亮相，热度始终不减。</p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F8675f464p00qyxxca009vc000n000t8m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F98cb979dp00qyxxce00f3c000u000u0m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p id=\"083QTL0T\">在综艺《蒙面舞王》中，关智斌以“暴走机器人”蒙面形象惊喜亮相，在排练过程中，即使练舞房就剩他一人，他仍在全力练习舞蹈，而且还十分尊重自己的舞台合作伙伴，不会以老牌艺人自居。尽管很快就被淘汰，正如节目的点评嘉宾容祖儿所说的，他是一个很努力的人。</p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F5570a82bp00qyxxc90050c000u000jbm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F88bf7fd8p00qyxxc9004yc000n000kvm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F1cfdd6a0j00qyxxc9001wc000gw00c2m.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p id=\"083QTL13\">最近，他又加盟一部新剧，从开机照中可以看出，他站在最边缘的位置，大概在剧中只是男三或男四的角色位置，与曾经热剧中的男一号相差甚远，但他依旧满面笑容，精神状态积极向上。在最近官宣的主流中秋晚会嘉宾中，关智斌更是以单人海报现身，足以证明他的努力付出并没有浪费。</p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2Feeab2eb1j00qyxxc9002jc000u0012sm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2Fd03022e5j00qyxxc9002ac000u000fum.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F0436c7cfp00qyxxcc00n3c000u00138m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p id=\"083QTL19\">除了勤奋拼事业，关智斌在外形保养上也是从不懈怠。不论是清爽的高颜值，还是充满肌肉线条美的好身材，虽不如出道之年的鲜嫩，却散发着成熟男性的魅力。</p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F92664fc3p00qyxxcb00cjc000u00168m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p id=\"083QTL1B\">相比关智斌，Boy\'z的另一位成员则不太如意。在组合出道之时，张致恒担任团队的队长，面孔青春帅气。可惜，在团队发展失利之后，张致恒更是身陷多个丑闻，先是被曝光一脚踏五船，辜负爱妻与孩子，随后与经纪公司解约之后，导致经济来源被完全切断。无奈下才向多位朋友借钱，因无力归还再度传出债务丑闻。</p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F8e76726bj00qyxxc9001gc000n0009ym.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F37f5d328p00qyxxcb0041c000gw00c2m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2Ff1c585ddp00qyxxca0016c000s5006gm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F801f06a2j00qyxxca005dc000u0019gm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p id=\"083QTL1J\">经历一段低谷之后，张致恒似乎重新振作。虽然形象完全走样，却开始努力减肥，积极前往内地参加小型商演，还经常在社交平台分享生活，与好友李日朗进行直播PK，偶尔也会直播带货，抓住一切机会来改善生活状态。</p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F7d1a9461p00qyxxcd004cc000fp00h5m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2Fbc1b8cb1p00qyxxcc006yc000n000hym.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F6a82b6e0j00qyxxcb0023c000u000hcm.jpg&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p id=\"083QTL1P\">因为名气大不如从前，再加上绯闻缠身，张致恒很难接到好资源。只能参加一些小地方的商演活动，甚至要和没名气的网红歌手进行示好。该网红发出两人的合影视频，在视频中，张致恒发福明显，穿着打扮略显邋遢，很难找到曾经那个阳光活力的男孩形象。</p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F8d923541p00qyxxcc006mc000n000lxm.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"f_center\"><img src=\"https://nimg.ws.126.net/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdingyue.ws.126.net%2F2021%2F0905%2F5b488a9dp00qyxxce00dxc000n000y4m.png&amp;thumbnail=650x2147483647&amp;quality=80&amp;type=jpg\"><br></p>\n<p id=\"083QTL1T\">虽然这些初代偶像人气不再，若是勤奋努力，仍然会有再度走红的机会，但要是自暴自弃，或是丑闻不断，即便是人气偶像，也不会拥有自己的舞台。</p>\n<p id=\"083QTL1U\"><strong>本文未经授权严禁转载违者必究！</strong></p>', '提到港圈的初代偶像男团，Boy\'z组合肯定位于前列，由成员张致恒和关智斌组成，两人出道时20多岁，不仅拥有高颜值，还充满活泼阳光的气质，在当时大受欢迎。如今Boy\'z组合早已解散，两位成员的发展现状也是相差悬殊。 作为成员之一的关智斌，已到不惑之年，但整体状态保持良好，事业重心基本转移